name: GLKTextureLoaderError.Code
desc: Values to be returned in an NSError when a texture loader encounters an error.

items.name: case fileOrURLNotFound
items.desc: A file could not be found at the path provided.

items.name: case invalidNSData
items.desc: The data provided is not in a recognized image format.

items.name: case unknownFileType
items.desc: The file was in an unrecognized format.

items.name: case pvrAtlasUnsupported
items.desc: Cube maps may not be compressed in PVRTC format.

items.name: case cubeMapInvalidNumFiles
items.desc: The incorrect number of files were specified for the cube map.

items.name: case compressedTextureUpload
items.desc: A compressed texture could not be uploaded.

items.name: case uncompressedTextureUpload
items.desc: An uncompressed texture could not be uploaded.

items.name: case unsupportedCubeMapDimensions
items.desc: The cube mapâ€™s dimensions are incorrect.

items.name: case unsupportedBitDepth
items.desc: The data in the source image has an unsupported bit depth.

items.name: case unsupportedPVRFormat
items.desc: The data in the PVRTC compressed format is in an unsupported format.

items.name: case dataPreprocessingFailure
items.desc: The data could not be preprocessed correctly.

items.name: case mipmapUnsupported
items.desc: The texture source data does not allow mipmaps to be generated.

items.name: case unsupportedOrientation
items.desc: The texture source data is stored with an unsupported origin position.

items.name: case reorientationFailure
items.desc: The texture source data does not allow the image to be reoriented.

items.name: case alphaPremultiplicationFailure
items.desc: The texture source data does not allow the alpha to be premultiplied.

items.name: case invalidEAGLContext
items.desc: The EAGL context was not a valid context.

items.name: case incompatibleFormatSRGB
items.desc: The decoded data was in an incompatible format for an sRGB texture.
